======================================================================
11. KNOWN LIMITATIONS
======================================================================

11.1 v0.1 Limitations (Honest)
--------------------------------
  Single GPU only
    Impact: No distributed training support
    Mitigation / Roadmap: v0.3 community contribution surface

  Heuristic router detection
    Impact: May miss custom MoE architectures
    Mitigation / Roadmap: Manual override config provided

  No weight-level analysis
    Impact: Cannot diagnose checkpoint quality statically
    Mitigation / Roadmap: model-clinic recommended for that use case

  No WandB / TensorBoard integration
    Impact: Requires separate logging setup
    Mitigation / Roadmap: v0.2 based on demand

  Python 3.8+ required
    Impact: Older environments not supported
    Mitigation / Roadmap: Documented clearly

  No automatic fix application
    Impact: Diagnosis only; fixes are manual
    Mitigation / Roadmap: Suggestions engine in v0.2

  Router pattern coverage
    Impact: DeepSeek-MoE not in v0.1
    Mitigation / Roadmap: v0.2 explicit target


11.2 Architectural Decisions with Trade-offs
---------------------------------------------
  - Ring buffer design caps memory footprint but loses older step data
    if buffer is too small.
  - Sampling every N steps misses intra-interval collapses — acceptable
    at default N=10.
  - CPU-side statistics computation avoids GPU overhead but adds
    host-device transfer latency.
  - Hook-based approach is model-agnostic but requires router output to
    be accessible as a tensor.


======================================================================
12. FUNCTIONS & CLASSES REFERENCE
======================================================================

  audit(model, dataloader, steps)
    Module: moewatch
    Description: Run full diagnostic pass. Returns AuditReport.

  MoEWatch(model, config)
    Module: moewatch
    Description: Training-time monitor. Attach to HF Trainer.

  WatchConfig(**kwargs)
    Module: moewatch.config
    Description: Configuration dataclass for all thresholds.

  HookManager
    Module: moewatch.hooks
    Description: Manages attach/detach lifecycle for all router hooks.

  RouterHook
    Module: moewatch.hooks
    Description: Forward hook capturing routing logits per step.

  StatCollector
    Module: moewatch.collector
    Description: Asynchronous aggregation of routing statistics.

  RingBuffer
    Module: moewatch.collector
    Description: Fixed-memory circular buffer for step data.

  EntropyAnalyzer
    Module: moewatch.analyzer
    Description: Computes Shannon entropy per layer per step.

  CollapseDetector
    Module: moewatch.analyzer
    Description: Dead/cold expert identification logic.

  AuditReport
    Module: moewatch.report
    Description: Structured report object with all diagnostic methods.

  CLIReporter
    Module: moewatch.report
    Description: Terminal ASCII formatter for human-readable output.

  report.summary()
    Module: AuditReport
    Description: Full human-readable diagnostic summary.

  report.dead_experts()
    Module: AuditReport
    Description: Returns list of dead and cold experts per layer.

  report.routing_entropy()
    Module: AuditReport
    Description: Per-layer entropy scores and trend.

  report.utilization()
    Module: AuditReport
    Description: Per-expert token distribution histogram.

  report.recommendations()
    Module: AuditReport
    Description: Actionable fix suggestions (v0.2).

  report.to_json()
    Module: AuditReport
    Description: Machine-readable JSON export.


======================================================================
13. COMPETITIVE POSITIONING (POST-RESEARCH)
======================================================================

  LibMoE (TMLR 2024)
    What It Does: Full MoE research framework with routing diagnostics
    and regime-level analysis
    What moewatch Adds: No framework adoption required

  model-clinic (v0.4.2)
    What It Does: Static weight analysis, 20+ conditions including
    moe_router_collapse detection
    What moewatch Adds: Live forward pass diagnostics, not checkpoint
    inspection

  chuk-lazarus (MLX)
    What It Does: MoEHooks with get_expert_utilization() and
    get_router_entropy() — Apple Silicon only
    What moewatch Adds: Identical goal, Linux/CUDA/PyTorch-native

  MLXLMProbe (MLX)
    What It Does: Router diagnostics on Apple Silicon, GPT-OSS only,
    macOS 15+ required
    What moewatch Adds: Same diagnostics for every HF MoE on any
    Linux/GPU

  WandB / TensorBoard
    What It Does: General training metric logging, no MoE-specific
    diagnostics
    What moewatch Adds: MoE-specific layer on top, complementary

  Custom scripts
    What It Does: Researcher one-off analysis code, not reusable,
    rediscovered per project
    What moewatch Adds: Reusable, maintained, pip-installable

Single-sentence positioning:
  moewatch is the only tool that lets you audit any existing
  HuggingFace MoE model with one pip install and one line of code —
  on any Linux/GPU environment, with live training-time diagnostics.


