======================================================================
15. SOLUTION SUMMARY
======================================================================

moewatch solves a confirmed, unoccupied gap in the MoE training
tooling ecosystem. The solution is precisely scoped, honestly
positioned, and designed to be composable with — not competitive
with — the tools that already exist.

  Expert collapse discovered after full training run
    Solution: Live dead expert detection during training, every 100
    steps

  Routing entropy not surfaced by standard logging
    Solution: Shannon entropy per layer, per step, with trend alerts

  No pip-installable tool for existing HF MoE models
    Solution: pip install moewatch + one line to attach

  Static-only tools (model-clinic) miss live dynamics
    Solution: Forward-pass hooks, not checkpoint weight inspection

  MLX tools exist but exclude Linux/CUDA researchers
    Solution: PyTorch-native, Linux-first, Colab-validated

  Researchers write one-off analysis scripts per project
    Solution: Maintained, reusable library with community surface


